'''Bahrain''' competed at the '''[[2009 Asian Youth Games|2009]] [[Asian Youth Games]]''' held in [[Singapore]] from June 29, 2009 to July 7, 2009. Bahrain sent 22 athletes who competed in 8 sports and was able to finish with 1 bronze medal.

